            <title>[JCR-1612] Reintroduce NamespaceStorage</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JCR-1612</link>
                <project id="10591" key="JCR">Jackrabbit Content Repository</project>
                        <description>hi jukka&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
i open this issue as a reminder of our recent discussion in basel:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
we decided that you will &lt;br/&gt;
- reintroduce the NamespaceStorage you recently removed from jcr2spi&lt;br/&gt;
- reintroduce a namespace cache in jcr2spi (but using a simple map instead of NamespaceCache object)&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
in addition we agreed that we want to share the NamespaceRegistryImpl between jcr2spi and jackrabbit-core&lt;br/&gt;
and you volenteered to provide a patch for that.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
thanks in advance&lt;br/&gt;
angela</description>
